President Trump has announced a commitment to the fight in Afghanistan, showing a dedication to ensuring the safety of the nation. Despite criticism from detractors, the decision reflects the need to clean up the mess left behind in Afghanistan over the past 15 years. Trump has listened to his commanders and asked tough questions, demonstrating his commitment to putting America First. While the military works on the ground, Trump will utilize diplomatic and economic tools to prevent Afghanistan from becoming a breeding ground for radical Islamic terrorism. The decision highlights Trump's leadership, trust in the military and diplomats, and faith in American citizens.